advancement.originalenhancement.root.tit: The end is also the beginning of a new life
advancement.originalenhancement.root.des: Eat the End Fruit(Can this thing be eaten?)
item.originalenhancement.wooden_sword_th: Wooden Sored--The Forest Of The End
item.originalenhancement.nature_apparatu: As the core of the apparatus, it controls the operation of the entire apparatus
item.originalenhancement.end_fruit.lore1: The fruit that appears with the fall of the ruler of The End, the energy contained in it will give the eater the end
item.originalenhancement.frostmourne.lor: Frotmourne is a weapon that can manipulate the user's mind and corrupt the user, and cannot and should not be in the hands of ordinary people. This one is a replica of Frotmourne, and the runes on the sword give it great power and the ability to steal the soul of the enemy, which makes it still an evil weapon.
Inflict heavy damage on non-undead mobs and heal users
item.originalenhancement.wooden_sword_lu: A forest that symbolizes the real world with strong vitality, and it can use its own energy to protect its holders
Add a flourishing effect for holders when they are attacked
item.originalenhancement.wooden_sword_th: The wooden sword of the Purple Song Forest symbolizing the End Place, the creatures hit by it will enter the End State
Attack have an additional The End effect
multiblock.originalenhancement.apparatus: The apparatus lacks the correct source of energy

multiblock.originalenhancement.converter: Items cannot be placed in the conversion disk in water
